<section id="link-header" data-speed="5" data-type="background">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-5 ">
        <h1>LINK</h1>
        <%= image_tag 'link-logo.png', class: 'img-responsive link-logo' %>
        <h3>City slicker, coffee house tripper, weekend kicker</h3>
        <p>Introducing LINK – A flat pedal for the race to the weekend and a clip-in side for the weekend races to the coffee shop.</p>
        <p>All in one TIME pedal.</p>

        <h3>LINK | 194g</h3>
        <p>Steel axle, composite body, ATAC EASY cleat</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-7 ">
        <%= image_tag 'link-hero-shadow.png', class: 'img-responsive link-pedal', alt: 'Link Commuter pedal', title: "Link city bike pedal" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="link-commute-trail">
  <div class="container-fluid">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-6" id="commute">
        <h1>Everyday, Casual Riding</h1>
        <%= image_tag 'link-riders-commute.png', class: 'img-responsive' %>
        <%= image_tag 'link-perspective-flat.png', class: 'img-responsive rider-pedals' %>
        <h3>On one side, a flat platform is a perfect fit for almost any casual ride giving you the freedom to bike and walk in the comfort of your favorite shoes.</h3>

      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6" id="trail">
        <h1>Sport, Trail Riding</h1>
        <%= image_tag 'link-riders-sport.png', class: 'img-responsive' %>
        <%= image_tag 'link-perspective-top.png', class: 'img-responsive rider-pedals' %>
        <h3>The other side has the ease and positive engagement of our ATAC system giving you extra pedaling efficiency when you find yourself on longer two-wheeled trips.</h3>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="counter-weight-cleats">
  <div class="container-fluid">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-6" id="counter-weight">
        <%= image_tag 'link-counterweight.png', class: 'img-responsive', style: 'width:30%;' %>
        <h1 class="text-center">a pedal with a preference</h1>
        <p class="text-center">Depending on your preferred type of the riding, the LINK comes with a counter-weight to let you choose which side of the pedal is right side up. Of course, either side is always a flip away.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6" id="link-cleat">
        <%= image_tag 'link-easy-cleat.png', class: 'img-responsive', style: 'width:30%;' %>
        <h1 class="text-center">ATAC EASY cleat</h1>
        <p class="text-center">Easy to setup and easy to use. The ATAC EASY cleat is a snap to install and gives you 10º of float when using the ATAC clip in side of the LINK pedal.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>